Example of crafting an intent to launch an exported activity:
`Intent intent = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_VIEW);
intent.setClassName("<TARGET_PACKAGE_NAME>", ".<EXPORTED_ACTIVITY_NAME>");
intent.putExtra("<PARAM_NAME>", "<VALUE>");
startActivity(intent);`

Example of sending a broadcast to an exported receiver:
`Intent intent = new Intent("<CUSTOM_ACTION_OR_BROADCAST_ACTION>");
intent.putExtra("<PARAM_NAME>", "<VALUE>");
sendBroadcast(intent);`

Example of binding to an exported service:
`Intent intent = new Intent();
intent.setClassName("<TARGET_PACKAGE_NAME>", ".<EXPORTED_SERVICE_NAME>");
bindService(intent, serviceConnection, Context.BIND_AUTO_CREATE);`

Example algorithm pseudocode: 
for each bit-offset:
  if it doesn't look like the start of a dynamic huffman block:
    skip this offset
  try decompressing from that offset:
    if the decompressed data looks plausible:
      return decompressed data!
  catch decompression errors:
    continue

